    "# Population Dynamics {background-color=\"#1a5276\"}\n",
    "\n",
    "## Exponential and Logistic Growth\n",
    "\n",
    "**Malthusian / Exponential growth** ([Malthus, 1798](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Robert_Malthus)):\n",
    "$$\\frac{dP}{dt} = rP, \\quad P(0)=P_0 \\quad\\Rightarrow\\quad P(t) = P_0 e^{rt}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Predicts unlimited growth ($r>0$) or extinction ($r<0$). Unrealistic long-term.\n",
    "\n",
    ". . .\n",
    "\n",
    "**Logistic growth** ([Verhulst, 1838](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pierre_Fran%C3%A7ois_Verhulst)):\n",
    "$$\\frac{dP}{dt} = rP\\!\\left(1-\\frac{P}{K}\\right), \\quad P(0)=P_0$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Exact solution: $\\displaystyle P(t) = \\frac{K}{1+\\left(\\dfrac{K}{P_0}-1\\right)e^{-rt}}$\n",
    "\n",
    "As $t\\to\\infty$: $P(t)\\to K$ — the **stable equilibrium** (carrying capacity).\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "## Logistic Growth: Solution Curves"
